title: About Me!
text: Hi! My name is Kate Cordes, and I am a student at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I am a journalism and sports media double major. Sports and writing are two of my favorite things, so I figured I would combine the two and create a little blog using the skills I’ve learned to answer the questions I’ve always wondered about. I hope you enjoy!
